      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "KID KERMARO (2) is a newcomer for the Gary Stewart kennel. Drawn well and should get his chance. Has a nice profile and expected to measure up at first outing. SHE'S A ANGEL (7) showed good early burn and was there until turning but swamped late to finish 7th at The Gardens in Maiden company. A forward showing wouldn't surprise. TRALEE TINY (8) still a maiden after 13 runs but rarely out of the placings. Finished fifth (19.12) at Dubbo latest but tends to run well here despite having never won. Cannot be left out. RUN ROLEX (1) is by Shima Shine out of Fusion Girl making debut. Drawn favourably and can capitalise. Can feature with the right run.",
